{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e7627531ec","title":"谢富治对外国专家局的指示","origin":"1967年9月7日红代会清华井冈山一部第三动态组编《动态》第143期。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3d17a4fe72","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"e7627531ec"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"93cca4665d","name":"谢富治","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"85b13f5c0b","name":"谢富治"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"68e3e30a3d","type":"title","text":"谢富治对外国专家局的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e7627531ec"},{"id":"1284e3e199","type":"authors","text":"谢富治","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e7627531ec"},{"id":"1be61849ee","type":"paragraph","text":"外国专家局要坚决制止武斗，恢复良好的革命秩序，造成良好的国际影响，为无产阶级文化大革命增光。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e7627531ec"},{"id":"e3fb11fa38","type":"paragraph","text":"傅崇碧副司令员批准五条意见大意是：外专局是接待外宾的单位，要坚决遵照我们伟大领袖毛主席的号召，坚持文斗，不要武斗，不准调人参加武斗，“抓革命，促生产”，立即恢复正常工作秩序。不准私自抓人。两派之间的分歧，采取“四大”的方式协商解决。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e7627531ec"},{"id":"4faa636de0","type":"appellation","text":"","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e7627531ec"}],"page":{"id":"24ed2c4223","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e7627531ec","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}